description:
An object showing available sizes for the media file. Example:{
  "sizes": {
    "thumb": {
      "h": 150,
      "resize": "crop",
      "w": 150
    },
    "large": {
      "h": 1366,
      "resize": "fit",
      "w": 2048
    },
    "medium": {
      "h": 800,
      "resize": "fit",
      "w": 1200
    },
    "small": {
      "h": 454,
      "resize": "fit",
      "w": 680
    }
  }
}
See Photo Media URL formatting for how to format a photo's URL, such as media_url_https, based on the available sizes.
